header.author-notes:
The mod is setting for display the dropdown box for anonymous users, 
	if you want enable it also for registered users :
		open : root/includes/function_quick_language.php
		find : define('QUICK_LANGUAGE_USER', false);
		replace with : define('QUICK_LANGUAGE_USER', true);	

	-------------------------------------------------------------------

	Need extra support ?
	--------------------
	You can contact me at http://www.mssti.com/phpbb3/

